---
import img1 from "../assets/about-7.png";
import img2 from "../assets/about-8.png";
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- ── Images block (left) ── -->
      <div class="relative order-1 lg:order-1">
        <!-- Main image -->
        <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-[4/3]">
          <img
            src={img1.src}
            alt="Vista principal Cabaña Deluxe Mística 2"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 via-transparent to-transparent rounded-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating thumbnail -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-4 sm:-right-8 w-36 sm:w-48 aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white">
          <img
            src={img2.src}
            alt="Interior Cabaña Deluxe Mística 2"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Feature pills -->
        <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[11px] font-bold bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-gray-800 shadow-md">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-users text-orange-400 text-[10px]"></i>
            Espacio familiar
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[11px] font-bold bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-gray-800 shadow-md">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-couch text-orange-400 text-[10px]"></i>
            Sala privada
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── Text block (right) ── -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 order-2 lg:order-2">

        <!-- Label -->
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-orange-400 uppercase">
          Alojamiento & Estancias
        </p>

        <!-- Title -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight leading-tight">
            Cabaña Deluxe Mística 2
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Para 5 – 6 personas · Valle Sagrado</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Perfecta para compartir y disfrutar de un espacio totalmente independiente, nuestras 
          <strong class="text-gray-800">Cabañas Deluxe</strong> ofrecen la combinación ideal de confort, amplitud y contacto con la naturaleza.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Equipadas con <strong class="text-gray-800">sala</strong>, refrigerador, termo, tazas y agua, te harán sentir como en casa, rodeadas de la serenidad del <em>Valle Sagrado</em>. Su ambiente cálido invita al descanso y la convivencia.
        </p>

        <!-- Amenities grid -->
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2.5">
          {[
            { icon: "fa-solid fa-couch",         text: "Sala de estar privada" },
            { icon: "fa-solid fa-snowflake",      text: "Refrigerador" },
            { icon: "fa-solid fa-mug-hot",        text: "Termo & tazas incluidos" },
            { icon: "fa-solid fa-droplet",        text: "Agua incluida" },
            { icon: "fa-solid fa-tree",           text: "Entorno de paz natural" },
            { icon: "fa-solid fa-face-smile",     text: "Estilo y privacidad" },
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-700 font-medium">
              <span class="w-7 h-7 flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg bg-orange-50 border border-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class={`${item.icon} text-orange-400 text-[11px]`}></i>
              </span>
              {item.text}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <hr class="border-gray-100" />

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-2">
          <a
            href="https://wa.link/ngq3h9"
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-6 py-3.5 bg-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-orange-300/40 transition-all duration-300 text-sm transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
            aria-label="Consultar disponibilidad Cabaña Deluxe Mística 2"
          >
            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-lg"></i>
            Consultar disponibilidad
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
